(librepcb_package 086cbff3-9add-439b-86c5-9792f5af0e25
 (name "TO-252")
 (description "TO-252, also known as DPAK or Decawatt Package, is a semiconductor package developed by Motorola for surface mounting on circuit boards. It represents a surface-mount variant of TO-251 package, and smaller variant of the D2PAK package. It is often used for high-power MOSFETs and voltage regulators.")
